  "instructions": [
    "Rinse the lentils and soak them in water for 30 minutes.",
    "Drain and cook the lentils in boiling water until they are tender.",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together the lemon juice, infuse oil, garlic, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Add the cooked lentils to the bowl and stir to combine.",
    "Stir in the chopped parsley and scallions.",
    "Taste and adjust the seasoning as needed.",
    "Spoon the salad into scallop shells and serve immediately.",
    "Garnish with additional parsley if desired."
